645
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:58,320
After my father left,

646
00:30:58,520 --> 00:31:00,000
we’re completely on our own.

647
00:31:00,320 --> 00:31:01,840
I failed to be admitted to a good school

648
00:31:02,040 --> 00:31:03,240
