The police unit does give
us some allowances.

650
00:31:07,520 --> 00:31:08,520
But it’s all my fault.

651
00:31:08,760 --> 00:31:09,480
I lost all the savings

652
00:31:09,600 --> 00:31:10,920
when running a small business,

653
00:31:11,120 --> 00:31:13,560
so when my sister
had the incident, we...

