713
00:33:23,400 --> 00:33:24,720
That means Xing Kelei

714
00:33:24,720 --> 00:33:26,560
has given his heart to her.

715
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:28,440
Perhaps they will

716
00:33:28,440 --> 00:33:29,720
get married.

717
00:33:30,760 --> 00:33:31,680
Married?

718
00:33:34,000 --> 00:33:35,640
