733
00:33:58,360 --> 00:34:00,000
to date a girl.

734
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:01,360
Right.

735
00:34:01,440 --> 00:34:02,560
So,

736
00:34:02,960 --> 00:34:04,160
this Mi Ka

737
00:34:04,200 --> 00:34:06,080
