00:35:24,560 --> 00:35:25,680
I’ll send the name to you later.

779
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:26,880
Who will use this?

780
00:35:27,680 --> 00:35:28,760
A friend of mine.

781
00:35:29,480 --> 00:35:30,560
