791
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,520
My idea is first

792
00:35:47,080 --> 00:35:49,000
you need to control well

793
00:35:49,080 --> 00:35:50,240
your emotion.

794
00:35:50,480 --> 00:35:52,440
You make mistakes
when you’re anxious.

795
00:35:52,840 --> 00:35:54,840
