863
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,280
I’ll stay here a bit longer.

864
00:39:11,400 --> 00:39:12,920
Kelei, thank you.

865
00:39:13,800 --> 00:39:15,520
Now you’re the only one

866
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,960
